"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5be32b0c6b344c6417e696388e443aef812c36","tid":1610833,"uid":321602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀！"},{"pid":"0c0447adead35cce8e128db326dfe00ce3bfdfe6","tid":1610833,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c77b0c0251528a2936553b5213adabdd7d0b6b3","tid":1610833,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"長知識 原來新型號手機可能有FM功被deactivate 左。有冇巴打對呢方面有研究？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/tag/how-to-unlock-fm-radio-hidden-smartphone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.makeuseof.com%2Ftag%2Fhow-to-unlock-fm-radio-hidden-smartphone%2F&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=eb79e88a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.makeuseof.com/tag/how-to-unlock-fm-radio-hidden-smartphone/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe ability to access the radio is a standard feature in the Qualcomm LTE modem, which is used in most of the world&rsquo;s smartphones. They most likely include this capability because using a smartphone to access the radio is common in the developing world.<br />\n<br />\nAnd it&rsquo;s simpler to deactivate the radio chip than to use completely different modems for phones sold in different areas."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"各位android用家可以試下條link講嘅NextRadio app嗎？<br />\n試完話我知得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ac959b204049bf84790768759f821482818cf0","tid":1610833,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"唔記得貼link <br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nextradioapp.nextradio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/li